Class Ticket

  • java.lang.Object
    • ticket.Ticket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class Ticket
extends java.lang.Object
implements Keyed<java.lang.Long>, Owned<Customer>, java.io.Serializable, Visitable
